		<li class="pingback even thread-even depth-1 clearfix" id="comment-58234">
		<div id="div-comment-58234" class="clearfix comment-container">
		<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<span class="authorname"><a href='https://creativecommons.org/weblog/entry/36917' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>CC Filmmakers and Festivals Change the Rules - Creative Commons</a></span>
