		September 28, 2013 at 2:50 pm</a>
        		 
		</div>
		<p>Well, re my comment above in support of copyleft, today, 8 months later, I changed all my stuff from CC-BY-SA to CC0. It wasn&#8217;t in response to any event; just a growing realisation that fighting copyright with copyright is like bombing for peace. You were right Nina; the law is an ass none of us should wish to ride.</p>
		</div>
</li><!-- #comment-## -->
